    "term": "Normalization of Workarounds",
    "definition": "The process by which informal fixes become embedded as standard operating behavior.",
    "notes": [
      "Often begins as adaptation",
      "Becomes invisible over time",
      "Reshapes governance reality"
    ]
  }
